# Fallback ENCRYPTION_KEY persisted to disk when the env var isn't set —
# see artifacts/api-server/crypto.py. Must never be committed: it decrypts
# every secret in the database (Telegram bot token, supplier API keys...).
artifacts/api-server/.encryption_key

